            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Nehemiah.1:1-3:14",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ENehemiah%201%3A1-3%3A14%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ENehemiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20memoirs%20of%20Nehemiah%20son%20of%20Hacaliah.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ENehemiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Concern%20for%20Jerusalem%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3EIn%20late%20autumn%2C%20in%20the%20month%20of%20Kislev%2C%20in%20the%20twentieth%20year%20of%20King%20Artaxerxes%26%23x2019%3B%20reign%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20month%20of%20Kislev%20of%20the%20twentieth%20year.%3C%2Fem%3E%20A%20number%20of%20dates%20in%20the%20book%20of%20Nehemiah%20can%20be%20cross-checked%20with%20dates%20in%20surviving%20Persian%20records%20and%20related%20accurately%20to%20our%20modern%20calendar.%20This%20month%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar%20occurred%20within%20the%20months%20of%20November%20and%20December%20446%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20%3Cem%3Etwentieth%20year%3C%2Fem%3E%20probably%20refers%20to%20the%20reign%20of%20King%20Artaxerxes%26%23xA0%3BI%3B%20compare%202%3A1%3B%205%3A14.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20I%20was%20at%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EHanani%2C%20one%20of%20my%20brothers%2C%20came%20to%20visit%20me%20with%20some%20other%20men%20who%20had%20just%20arrived%20from%20Judah.%20I%20asked%20them%20about%20the%20Jews%20who%20had%20returned%20there%20from%20captivity%20and%20about%20how%20things%20were%20going%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThings%20are%20not%20going%20well%20for%20those%20who%20returned%20to%20the%20province%20of%20Judah.%20They%20are%20in%20great%20trouble%20and%20disgrace.%20The%20wall%20of%20Jerusalem%20has%20been%20torn%20down%2C%20and%20the%20gates%20have%20been%20destroyed%20by%20fire.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20I%20heard%20this%2C%20I%20sat%20down%20and%20wept.%20In%20fact%2C%20for%20days%20I%20mourned%2C%20fasted%2C%20and%20prayed%20to%20the%20God%20of%20heaven.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20said%2C%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20God%20of%20heaven%2C%20the%20great%20and%20awesome%20God%20who%20keeps%20his%20covenant%20of%20unfailing%20love%20with%20those%20who%20love%20him%20and%20obey%20his%20commands%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3Elisten%20to%20my%20prayer!%20Look%20down%20and%20see%20me%20praying%20night%20and%20day%20for%20your%20people%20Israel.%20I%20confess%20that%20we%20have%20sinned%20against%20you.%20Yes%2C%20even%20my%20own%20family%20and%20I%20have%20sinned!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20have%20sinned%20terribly%20by%20not%20obeying%20the%20commands%2C%20decrees%2C%20and%20regulations%20that%20you%20gave%20us%20through%20your%20servant%20Moses.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BPlease%20remember%20what%20you%20told%20your%20servant%20Moses%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BIf%20you%20are%20unfaithful%20to%20me%2C%20I%20will%20scatter%20you%20among%20the%20nations.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20if%20you%20return%20to%20me%20and%20obey%20my%20commands%20and%20live%20by%20them%2C%20then%20even%20if%20you%20are%20exiled%20to%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20earth%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eof%20the%20heavens.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20I%20will%20bring%20you%20back%20to%20the%20place%20I%20have%20chosen%20for%20my%20name%20to%20be%20honored.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20people%20you%20rescued%20by%20your%20great%20power%20and%20strong%20hand%20are%20your%20servants.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EO%26%23xA0%3BLord%2C%20please%20hear%20my%20prayer!%20Listen%20to%20the%20prayers%20of%20those%20of%20us%20who%20delight%20in%20honoring%20you.%20Please%20grant%20me%20success%20today%20by%20making%20the%20king%20favorable%20to%20me.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A11%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Etoday%20in%20the%20sight%20of%20this%20man.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Put%20it%20into%20his%20heart%20to%20be%20kind%20to%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3EIn%20those%20days%20I%20was%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20cup-bearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_1%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ENehemiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ENehemiah%20Goes%20to%20Jerusalem%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EEarly%20the%20following%20spring%2C%20in%20the%20month%20of%20Nisan%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20month%20of%20Nisan.%3C%2Fem%3E%20This%20month%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar%20occurred%20within%20the%20months%20of%20April%20and%20May%20445%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20during%20the%20twentieth%20year%20of%20King%20Artaxerxes%26%23x2019%3B%20reign%2C%20I%20was%20serving%20the%20king%20his%20wine.%20I%20had%20never%20before%20appeared%20sad%20in%20his%20presence.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_2%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20king%20asked%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20are%20you%20looking%20so%20sad%3F%20You%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20look%20sick%20to%20me.%20You%20must%20be%20deeply%20troubled.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EThen%20I%20was%20terrified%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_3%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20I%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLong%20live%20the%20king!%20How%20can%20I%20not%20be%20sad%3F%20For%20the%20city%20where%20my%20ancestors%20are%20buried%20is%20in%20ruins%2C%20and%20the%20gates%20have%20been%20destroyed%20by%20fire.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_4%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20asked%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWell%2C%20how%20can%20I%20help%20you%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EWith%20a%20prayer%20to%20the%20God%20of%20heaven%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_5%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20it%20please%20the%20king%2C%20and%20if%20you%20are%20pleased%20with%20me%2C%20your%20servant%2C%20send%20me%20to%20Judah%20to%20rebuild%20the%20city%20where%20my%20ancestors%20are%20buried.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_6%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%2C%20with%20the%20queen%20sitting%20beside%20him%2C%20asked%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHow%20long%20will%20you%20be%20gone%3F%20When%20will%20you%20return%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20After%20I%20told%20him%20how%20long%20I%20would%20be%20gone%2C%20the%20king%20agreed%20to%20my%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_7%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20also%20said%20to%20the%20king%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20it%20please%20the%20king%2C%20let%20me%20have%20letters%20addressed%20to%20the%20governors%20of%20the%20province%20west%20of%20the%20Euphrates%20River%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20province%20beyond%20the%20river%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%202%3A9.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20instructing%20them%20to%20let%20me%20travel%20safely%20through%20their%20territories%20on%20my%20way%20to%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_8%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20please%20give%20me%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20Asaph%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20forest%2C%20instructing%20him%20to%20give%20me%20timber.%20I%20will%20need%20it%20to%20make%20beams%20for%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20Temple%20fortress%2C%20for%20the%20city%20walls%2C%20and%20for%20a%20house%20for%20myself.%26%23x201D%3B%20And%20the%20king%20granted%20these%20requests%2C%20because%20the%20gracious%20hand%20of%20God%20was%20on%20me.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_9%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20I%20came%20to%20the%20governors%20of%20the%20province%20west%20of%20the%20Euphrates%20River%2C%20I%20delivered%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20letters%20to%20them.%20The%20king%2C%20I%20should%20add%2C%20had%20sent%20along%20army%20officers%20and%20horsemen%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Echarioteers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20protect%20me.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_2_10%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20Sanballat%20the%20Horonite%20and%20Tobiah%20the%20Ammonite%20official%20heard%20of%20my%20arrival%2C%20they%20were%20very%20displeased%20that%20someone%20had